gurmukhi: ਅਗਨਿ ਬਾੲਿ ਜਲੇ ਥਲੇ ਮਹਿ ਸਰਬ ਠੳੁਰ ਨਿਵਾਸ ||੮||੧੮੮||
transliteration: Agad(i) Bade Jale Thale Maih Sarab Thaur Nivaas||8||188||
translation: He abides at all the places including fire, air, water and earth.8.188.

gurmukhi: ਦੇਹ ਗੇਹ ਨ ਨੇਹ ਸਨੇਹ ਅਬੇਹ ਨਾਥ ਅਜੀਤ ||
transliteration: Deh Geh Na Neh Saneh Abeh Naath Ajeet||
translation: He hath no affection for body or love for home, He is Invincible and Unconquerable Lord.

gurmukhi: ਸਰਬ ਗੰਜਨ ਸਰਬ ਭੰਜਨ ਸਰਬ ਤੇ ਅਨਭੀਤ ||
transliteration: Sarab Gadjan Sarab Bhanjan Sarab Te Anbhoot||
translation: He is Destroyer and defacer of all, He is without malice and Merciful to all.

gurmukhi: ਸਰਬ ਕਰਤਾ ਸਰਬ ਹਰਤਾਸ ਸਰਬ ਦਯਾਲ ਅਦ੍ਵੇਖ ||
transliteration: Sarab Kartaa Sarab Hartaa Sarab Dhaat Advekh||
translation: He is Creator and Destroyer of all, He is without malice and Merciful to all.

gurmukhi: ਚੱਕ੍ਰ੍ਰੁ ਚਿਹਨ ਨ ਬਰਨ ਜਾ ਕੋ ਜਾਤਿ ਪਾਤਿ ਨ ਭੇਖ ||੯||
transliteration: Chakkra Chihan Na Baran Jaa Ko Jaat(i) Paat(i) Na Bhekh||9||189||
translation: He is without mark, sign, and colour; He is without caste, linege and guise.9.189.

gurmukhi: ਰੂਪ ਰੇਖ ਨ ਰੰਗ ਜਾ ਕੋ ਰਾਗ ਰੂਪ ਨ ਰੰਗ ||
transliteration: Roop Rekh Na Ran Jaa Ko Raag Roop Na Ran||
translation: He is without form, line and colour, and hath no affection for sond and beauty.

gurmukhi: ਸਰਬ ਲਾੲਿਕ ਸਰਬ ਘਾੲਿਕ ਸਰਬ ਤੇ ਅਨਭੰਗ ||
transliteration: Sarab Laaik Sarab Ghaaik Sarab Te Anbhan||
translation: He is capable to do everything, He is the Destroyer of all and cannot be vanquished by anyone.

gurmukhi: ਸਰਬ ਦਾਤਾ ਸਰਬ ਗਯਾਤਾ ਸਰਬ ਕੋ ਪ੍ਰਤਿਪਾਲ ||
transliteration: Sarab Daataa Sarab Gyaataa Sarab Ko Pratipaal||
translation: He is the Donor, Knower and Sustainer of all.

gurmukhi: ਦੀਨ ਬੰਧੁ ਦਯਾਲ ਸੁਅਾਮੀ ਅਾਦਿ ਦੇਵ ਅਪਾਲ ||੧੦||੧੯੦||
transliteration: Deen Bandh(u) Dyaal Suaamee Aadh Dev Apaal||10||190||
translation: He is the friend of the poor, He is the beneficent Lord and patronless Primal Deity.10.190.

gurmukhi: ਦੀਨ ਬੰਧੁ ਪ੍ਰਬੀਨ ਸ੍ਰੀ ਪਤਿ ਸਰਬ ਕੋ ਕਰਤਾਰ ||
transliteration: Deen Bandh(u) Prabeen Sree Pat(i) Sarab Ko Kartaar||
translation: He, the adept Lord of maya, is the friend of the lowly and Creator of all.

gurmukhi: ਬਰਨ ਚਿਹਨ ਨ ਚੱਕ੍ਰ ਜਾ ਕੋ ਚੱਕ੍ਰ ਚਿਹਨ ਅਕਾਰ ||
transliteration: Baran Chihan Na Chakkra Jaa Ko Chakkra Chihan Akaar||
translation: He is without colour, mark and sign; He is without mark, sing and form.

gurmukhi: ਜਾਤਿ ਪਾਤਿ ਨ ਗੋਤ੍ਰ ਗਾਥਾ ਰੂਪ ਰੇਖ ਨ ਬਰਨ ||
transliteration: Jaat(i) Paat(i) Na Gotra Gadthaa Roop Rekh Na Baran||
translation: He is without caste , lineage and story of descent; He is without form, line and colour.

gurmukhi: ਸਰਬ ਦਾਤਾ ਸਰਬ ਗਯਾਤਾ ਸਰਬ ਭੂਅ ਕੋ ਭਰਨ ||੧੧||੧੯੧||
transliteration: Sarab Daataa Sarab Gadataa Sarab Bhooa Ko Bharan||11||191||
translation: He is the Donor and Knower of all and the Sustainer of all the universe. 11.191.

gurmukhi: ਦੁਸਟ ਗੰਜਨ ਸੱਤ੍ਰੁ ਭੰਜਨ ਪਰਮ ਪੁਰਖ ਪ੍ਰਮਾਥ ||
transliteration: Doust Gadjan Sattru Bhanjan Param Purakh(u) Pramaath||
translation: He is the Destroyer of the tyrants and vanquisher of the enemies, and the Omnipotent Supreme Purusha.
